    ## Tooltip Position
    {: #position }

    Control the display position of your tip.  By defualt, tips are positioned above the the element you are tiping.  Positioning allows you to modify that with the these classes. Just append modifier classes to the `.has-tip` class.

  table.table
    tr
      td
        markdown:
          [Hover here](#){: class="has-tip tip--top" data-tip="I'm on the top."}
      td
        markdown:
          `.has-tip.tip--top`
      td Top
    tr
      td
        markdown:
          [Hover here](#){: class="has-tip tip--right" data-tip="I'm on the right."}
      td
        markdown:
          `.has-tip.tip--right`
      td Right
    tr
      td
        markdown:
          [Hover here](#){: class="has-tip tip--bottom" data-tip="I'm on the bottom."}
      td
        markdown:
          `.has-tip.tip--bottom`
      td Bottom
    tr
      td
        markdown:
          [Hover here](#){: class="has-tip tip--left" data-tip="I'm on the left."}
