      td Anchored Right, Bottom

section.docs-section
  markdown:
    ## Multiline Tooltips
    {: #multiline }

    Multiline allows you to show more than a single line tooltip. Adding the `.tip--multiline` class will give you a tooltip that wraps at 200px wide. All other modifier classes may be used in combination with multi-line for more control.

  table.table
    tr
      td
        markdown:
          [Hover here](#){: class="has-tip tip--multiline" data-tip="I am God's vessel. But my greatest pain in life is that I will never be able to see myself perform live. - Kanye West"}
      td
        markdown:
          `.has-tip.tip--multiline`
      td
        markdown:
          _Oh, Kanye..._

